const ApplicantDashboard = () => { const { user } = useAuth(); // Mock data - replace with actual API calls const stats = { profileCompletion: 75, totalApplications: 3, activeApplications: 2, completedApplications: 1, unreadMessages: 5, }; const recentApplications = [ { id: 1, type: 'job', title: 'Software Engineer', company: 'Google', status: 'submitted', progress: 100, date: '2024-01-20', }, { id: 2, type: 'scholarship', title: 'MBA Scholarship', university: 'Harvard', status: 'in_progress', progress: 60, date: '2024-01-18', }, { id: 3, type: 'scholarship', title: 'PhD Fellowship', university: 'MIT', status: 'draft', progress: 25, date: '2024-01-15', }, ]; const quickActions = [ { title: 'Complete Profile', description: 'Finish setting up your profile', icon: User, href: '/profile', color: 'bg-blue-500', urgent: stats.profileCompletion < 100, }, { title: 'Browse Jobs', description: 'Find job opportunities', icon: Briefcase, href: '/jobs', color: 'bg-green-500', }, { title: 'Browse Scholarships', description: 'Find scholarship opportunities', icon: GraduationCap, href: '/scholarships', color: 'bg-purple-500', }, { title: 'Start Application', description: 'Begin a new application', icon: Plus, href: '/wizard/job', color: 'bg-orange-500', }, ]; const getStatusIcon = (status) => { switch (status) { case 'submitted': return ; case 'in_progress': return ; case 'draft': return ; default: return ; } }; const getStatusColor = (status) => { switch (status) { case 'submitted': return 'text-green-600 bg-green-100'; case 'in_progress': return 'text-yellow-600 bg-yellow-100'; case 'draft': return 'text-gray-600 bg-gray-100'; default: return 'text-gray-600 bg-gray-100'; } }; return (
